      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a museum-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in Carbon Black Metallic. This specimen features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and a tactile 6-speed manual gearbox. Mechanically perfected with proactive rod bearing replacement, a comprehensive VANOS overhaul, and a reinforced rear subframe to ensure chassis rigidity. The suspension remains factory-spec and taut, paired with a variable M-differential for precise torque distribution. The interior is impeccable with flawless Nappa leather and zero pixel degradation. Accompanied by a meticulous service dossier, this is an investment-grade example for the purist seeking peak analog performance.",
