      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that redefines the standard for 'showroom condition.' This car has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled environment, seeing only fair-weather weekend drives. The exterior paint retains its deep, factory luster thanks to a professional ceramic coating, showing zero rock chips, scratches, or swirl marks. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the premium leather remains supple and taut with absolutely no wear on the seat bolsters or steering wheel, and it still carries that distinct new-car aroma. It has never been smoked in and has never seen a drop of rain. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, with a comprehensive, open-checkbook service history documented from day one. Every button, sensor, and mechanical component functions exactly as intended. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning collector or enthusiast to own a specimen that looks, feels, and drives as if it just left the factory floor. All original keys, manuals, and service records are included.",
